text: Cañas Gordas is a corregimiento in Renacimiento District, Chiriquí Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 3,090 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 2,448; its population as of 2000 was 2,682. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Chiriquí Province
